HEADWORD: Sipunculacea
<hw>Si*pun`cu*la"ce*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>
<ety>[NL., from <ets>Sipunculus</ets>, the typical genus. See
<er>Siphuncle</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A suborder of
